Class LinkedList<T>

java.lang.Object
model.LinkedList<T>
Type Parameters:
T - nodes can hold any object
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<T>
public class LinkedList<T> extends Object implements Iterable<T>
A Singly Linked List with last and first node. It is iterable through a For-Each
